Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:27.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見られてる　どこからか…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:27.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll all use the closest exit, \Nand bust in from beside the central stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とりあえず　キルアを待とう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And the stronger the Nen, \Nthe bigger my stomach gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:26.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よぉ　待たせたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:26.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I should ask Leol-sama for a larger reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:30.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}感じるだろ　べっとりと へばりつくような視線。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:30.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right, Shidore?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:35.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人間特有の湿り具合だ。 やっぱり　みんな　気づいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:35.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Having a peon that understands \Nspeech is useful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:40.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　こんな距離から 気づかれてるようじゃ 大した奴らじゃ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:40.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You really need to talk more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見られてるな。 ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have permission to shoot her on sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア！ お待た。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As a foreigner, she can't blend \Nin with the other citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}街らしき影は　全然見えないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn! Damn that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうなんだけど みんな　似た方角に向かったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:58.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふん…　あっちか　こっちだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:58.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:06.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも問題は　何で　こっちを 見張ってるかってことだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:06.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How many times have I told you \Nnot to use your cell phone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:10.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確かに…。 さて　行くか！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:10.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The radio waves irritate my ears, \Nand it gives me a headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:14.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見てる奴が　どんな奴だろうと まずは情報収集だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:14.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Plus, I can hear what you're saying. Next time I catch you, I'll snap your \Nphone and your arm in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:20.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}で　どうだった？ ん？ お前のセーブデータさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:20.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}W-Well... There are urgent matters \Nthat must be dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I need to use my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:28.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カード　何枚ぐらい入ってた？ 一枚も入ってなかった。 えっ　マジ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:28.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's so urgent that you find \Nthe woman who ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　ジンからの メッセージはあったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can find her for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:36.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何て？ 「ゲームを楽しめ」って。 「ゲームを楽しめ」か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:36.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}R-Really? My nose happens to be very sharp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:41.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　ここがゲームの中だって実感 全然ないけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:41.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you have something she wore, I can track her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:46.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック。 キルアは　このゲームのルール 聞いて　どう思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:46.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Royal Guard appreciates the work you do, and I respect you, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:50.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん… まだ　全く未知数って感じだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:50.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So, a little give-and-take will benefit us both here. O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:03.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だ？　今の… 念能力かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:03.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I will become the King behind the scenes. To accomplish that, I must be friendly \Nwith Bizeff, not with the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:09.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君達　ゲームは初めてだろ。 さて　どうかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:09.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Welfin-sama, an urgent alert has been issued. Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本を持ってるってことは あんたもプレーヤーだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When peons send transmissions, \Nit gives me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フン　とぼけても無駄さ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This smells like... Taragette's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲーム初心者なのは　バレバレ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are bloodstains and dirty shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここは 「スティール」のカードで…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An intruder! If he took his shoes off here \Nto avoid leaving footprints, he must be somewhere deeper within.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一体　何してやがるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He didn't hide his shoes because he had a pressing mission and \Ncouldn't afford to lose time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:37.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふん　キルアくんと　ゴンくんか。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:37.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That day last week, when it rained?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:41.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で名前が分かったの？ さて　何でかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:41.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was the day Taragette went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヘヘヘ…　スペルカードも 知らないようじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm pretty sure that the intruder killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}話にならないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that means he disposed of Taragette's body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:05:03.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}決定的だな こいつら　来たばかりの 完全初心者　しかもガキ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:05:03.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he wrapped the body in something to move it, he must have come prepared. Was kidnapping a soldier his mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:06.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつらに　このスペルを 使うのは　もったいない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:06.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why would they do that?! Damn, I don't get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:13.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「トレース」で十分！ 「トレース」オン！ キルアを攻撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:13.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should I ask Shaiapouf for advice? No, I'll catch the intruder, \Nand get the answers from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:21.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームのスペルからは どうやったって逃げらんねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:21.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He did head inside the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:26.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！ キルア！　大丈夫!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:26.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This guy comes before Bizeff's woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:29.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヘヘヘ…　攻撃成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:29.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつ…　ヤバい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「リターン」オン！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's K-K-Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マサドラへ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you please tell me what your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:02.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}シズク　コルトピ ちょっと　いいかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:02.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't wait to play him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:13.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうせ　本拠地に戻っても 予定はないだろ？ そんなに　ゲームを クリアしたいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:13.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実は　ゲームのクリアが 目的じゃないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A nameless king... in a borrowed castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:21.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」の活動に 関係ありってこと？ まぁね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:21.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My subjects are mindless puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:29.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かった。 いいよ。 キルア　体のほう大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:29.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If this is the fate that the \Nheavens have granted me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:36.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？　別に変わりはないぜ。 でも心配だな。 何かされたのは 間違いないんだし。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:36.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have no doubt that I shall \Nbe slowly bored to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}魔法？　どんな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:52.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さぁな　まぁ　そのうち分かるだろ。 うん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:52.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！　街だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do not make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}懸賞って　あれのことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now we've all been beaten by the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:10.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ！　これ全部　懸賞？ …みてぇだな。 あっ　キルア！　あれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:10.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King says your En is irritating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「アントキバ月例大会行事表」…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I figured he would be saying that soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今月は　ジャンケン大会だってさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I can't remove our security...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:19.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}優勝賞品は「真実の剣」。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:19.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then you go and tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}重要なアイテムなのかな？ 恐らくな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't want another beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっち見てみ。 ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How does this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっちにも。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We can block all aura in a radius \Nsurrounding Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:34.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}参加してみる？ 当然。 じゃあ　せっかくだから いろんな懸賞に挑戦しようよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:34.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This way, my presence will not bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}情報収集も しなきゃいけないしな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you telling me to stay in one place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:45.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いらっしゃい！ ３０分以内に完食すれば お代はタダ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:45.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}the aura-free zone around me \Nwhile I move wouldn't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:48.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さらに　賞品の「ガルガイダー」を プレゼント！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:48.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I refuse to have my movement \Nconstantly monitored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでは　スタート！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, that would not be our proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねぇ　おっちゃん 魔法って　どうやったら使えんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So if I do not wish to deal with your presence, \NI will only be able to move
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だ？　そりゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}within that confined area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:04.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあ　この街で 一番の物知りって誰？ モノシリ？　何だ？　そりゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:04.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I must order you to move that zone \Nshould I wish to go elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この人　何も知らないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There is nothing more I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:11.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱり 単なるゲームキャラなんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:11.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Keep your En focused outside the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:17.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アイヤ！　やられたね！ はい！　賞品の「ガルガイダー」ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:17.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I shall put up with that until tomorrow's selection. Are you dissatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:23.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「１２１７　Ｆ－１８５」。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:23.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should that not suffice to guard \Nagainst outside attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:28.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これ　何のことだろう？ 君達　カード　初めてなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:28.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Or are you saying that there \Nare already enemies inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:34.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}左の数字は アイテムのカードナンバーで 右のほうは　記号が アイテムの入手難度のことね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:34.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That would be admitting that your En\N is completely worthless, would it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:38.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}難易度ランクは　ＳＳからＨまで １０段階あって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:38.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:41.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ｆは　下から３番目ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:41.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If my En is focused only outside, it cannot detect
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:46.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}記号の横の数字は　アイテムの カード化限度枚数のことね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:46.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}any attack from underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:51.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん　つまり このアイテムカードは…。 まぁ　くずアイテムかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:51.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In addition, my En is not capable of recognizing \Nan enemy that is already inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ！ キャ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you mean Komugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:09:07.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わぁ！ うわ！ あっ！ あっ！ 初めて見る顔だ… むごいのぉ 一緒にゲームに参加した奴だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:09:07.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, eleven soldiers still remain within the palace, and they are free to enter and leave at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:18.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねぇ　何があったの？ 突然　体が爆発したんだ 内側から　ボンとよ。 ゲームに参加して　まだ数時間 もう犠牲者が…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:18.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A check is performed each time someone enters, but if the soldier were being \Ncontrolled by the enemy, it would be difficult to know for sure. That means—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:23.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この圧倒的な死体の存在感 とてもゲームとは思えない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:23.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Enough. You may use En on the first floor of the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:27.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実際に 命の危険を伴うゲーム…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:27.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That will permit you to guard \Nagainst any underground attack! Tell everyone that no one is allowed \Non the second floor or above.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:35.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}消えた！ 現実世界に戻ったんだろ ゲームオーバーさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:35.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should an intruder come, I shall \Ndeal with them personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねぇ　キルア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Likewise, you will not come unless summoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさか　さっき　キルアが かけられた魔法って…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you disturb me, it will \Nhave violent consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:44.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分からない…。 安心しな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:44.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The other Ants
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:48.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲームに そんなスペルは存在しない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:48.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}were never allowed on or above the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:53.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スペル？ 君が言う　魔法のようなものだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:53.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But where do I go now? The central stairway connecting the \Nfirst and second floors, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:10:00.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつが死んだのは 他のプレーヤーによる 「念」のせいだ。 「念」？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:10:00.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If an intruder comes from underground, you will be in position to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:04.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それって　プレーヤー同士で 殺し合いをしてるってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:04.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Still, the King's been in a bad mood lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:11.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一体　何で？ プレーヤー狩りさ。 プレーヤー狩り？ 詳しいことは　後で教えてやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:11.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is he upset about losing \Nall those Gungi matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それより　俺達と組まないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have an idea as to the cause of his irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:20.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確実に　ゲームを クリアできる方法がある。 えっ？ 興味があるなら　ついて来てくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:20.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My ability, Spiritual Message, would be \Nable to confirm my suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:27.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この先に　俺の仲間もいる。 どうする？ うん　うさんくさいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:27.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, that would be an insult to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:30.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スタート直後に もう嫌な目に遭ってるし。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:30.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I'm just making excuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君は　確か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The truth is that I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:37.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここに来る途中　他のプレーヤーに スペルの攻撃を受けてたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:37.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So afraid of what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:46.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしかして　ずっと見てたの？ 俺達のこと。 ああ　俺だけじゃ　ない。 さまざまな連中が あのスタート地点を見張っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:46.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that grows inside the King even as we speak, I cannot bear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:54.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君を攻撃したスペルについてもね。 やけに気前がいいね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:54.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tsk, the rain washed away the scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何か　裏があるとしか思えないぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But now I have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:05.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やむを得ないのさ。 このゲームの難しさ いやらしさ　恐ろしさ それが分かって初めて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:05.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The intruder hid here to \Ncheck the second floor, but instead of going upstairs, he exited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:09.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達の誘いに 耳を貸すようになるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:09.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Something made him give up his mission? Or did he accomplish his objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:13.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　とにかく　初めて 来たばかりの君達にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:13.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, he may have used his power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}情報を聞くだけでも 有意義だと思うがね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I should probably warn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:22.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で　初めてだって思うの？ 途中でゲームから抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:22.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If any of you go to the second \Nfloor, the King will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:24.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}また　戻って来たのかも しれないだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:24.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tell everyone else in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:33.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これが　君達が 初心者だという証拠だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:33.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What if the intruder has the power to fly? The shoes and scent could have \Nbeen there to mislead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:38.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}慣れた者なら　相手が バインダーを出したら　すぐ 自分もバインダーを出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:38.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He could have flown up to the second floor! Youpi-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スペルカードでしか 防げないからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? Uh, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:44.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ってことは　キルアが かけられたスペルも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:44.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou is monitoring the palace with En.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:48.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カードでしか防げない。 たとえ　カードを 持ってなかったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:48.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If they'd gone to the second floor, \Nthey would have been caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:52.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バインダーを出す！ ハッタリは大事だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:52.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ah, sorry... It's not important. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:58.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック。 ねぇ　スペルのカードは どうやって手に入れるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:58.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That doesn't make sense! Then how did the intruder reach the stairway?! Youpi-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:03.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最も簡単なのは 魔法都市　マサドラへ行くことだ。 マサドラ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:03.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? What is it? Has Pitou-dono ever ceased to use En?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:07.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((「リターン」オン！ マサドラへ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:07.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For example, that day last week when it rained?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　行ってみようよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? You didn't hear what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアにかけられた スペルも気になるし。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There was a huge uproar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King tore off his own arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou had to heal the King, \Nso Pouf was using his En instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これで全部か？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wouldn't it be just as large as Pitou's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあ　始めようか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I'd guess that Pouf's En only \Nreached as far as the stairway. The intruder saw that aura, and gave up on ascending!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:46.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}たった今　また一人 プレーヤーがやられた。 君達と時を同じくして来た人物だ。 腹が　ふっ飛んでたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:46.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That all makes sense. The question is what the \Nintruder's objective was, and whether he's still hiding around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:49.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ボマーの仕業だ。 ボマー？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:49.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do I tell Youpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:52.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼の死は スペルによるものではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:52.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲームのスペルの中には
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I should report this to Pitou or Pouf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人を殺傷する類いのものは 一つもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pouf would be the best choice. And if possible, I need to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:02.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}故に　君達が かけられたスペルで負傷したり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:02.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}what the intruder's objective was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:05.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ましてや 死ぬことなど　あり得ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:05.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Otherwise, my report would be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:11.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スペルは　全部で４０種類。 その中で 君達が受けたスペルは　調査型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:11.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that the intruder somehow \Nmade it inside the palace, but turned and ran when he felt Pouf's En. I won't get any credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:18.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「トレース」か 「アドヒージョン」のいずれか。 ひと言で言うと そのスペルをかけられた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:18.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can make up an objective, but if the intruder is captured, \Nthey'll find out I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:31.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プレーヤーの情報が 全て　敵に筒抜けになる。 そうか　それで　あの時… それらのスペルを 新参プレーヤーにかけるため
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:31.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if I tell the Royal Guard my suspicions \Nand the intruder is never found, it would only waste their time \Nand damage my own standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:34.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スタート地点で 見張ってる連中がいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:34.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is that Bizeff's cell phone again?! I have a great idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:39.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　貴重なカードを手に入れたら すぐに現れ　強奪する。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:39.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So the intruder captured one of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:43.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最悪の場合は 命を落とすこともある。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:43.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}According to Leol, that intruder \Nhas the ability to teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:47.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さっきの奴みたいにか？ 俺は　そう簡単に　やられねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:47.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe that he and the \Nwoman are working together. They probably teleported out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:57.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プレーヤー狩りを目的とした 最も過激な奴ら　その中の１人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:57.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, but why would they do that? Yes, that's the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:00.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ボマー」と呼ばれる奴の仕業だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:00.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, I've discerned their objective. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:05.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ボマー…。 このゲームで アイテムカードをゲットする方法は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:05.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To blow up the palace. That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:09.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大きく分けて３つ それが分かるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:09.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? We must tell the Royal Guard! Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん…　自分で探す！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't be in such a rush. We can tell them after we've found the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:20.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他のプレーヤーから奪う。 うん　大きく分ければ　その３つだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:20.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's no time! Calm down, and consider this \Nfrom their perspective... Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:25.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし最近　他のプレーヤーから 強引に奪う者が増えて来た。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:25.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If they want to blow up the palace, \Nthey'll wait until they're sure the King is here. When would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:31.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}原因は　カードの入手難度と カード化限度枚数のシステムだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:31.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When all the citizens have assembled... Right before the ceremony begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:34.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自力でカードを 入手できない者達が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:34.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There will be five million humans! What a sight that will be to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}力ずくで他の者のカードを奪う。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just imagine looking down on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:40.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　抵抗する者は簡単に殺す。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:40.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King would not allow a double \Nto steal that gratification from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:44.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺せば指輪は消滅し カードデータも消えるが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:44.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So he will be there in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:48.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その分　カード化できる アイテムが増えるからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:48.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's only logical to assume the enemy \Nreached the same conclusion. True...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:52.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手を殺してしまったら カードは奪えない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:52.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've stood at the former Supreme Leader's \Nside for many of these celebrations...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:57.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}当初　このルールは　プレーヤー同士の 殺し合い防止が目的だったはず。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:57.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The experience brings indescribable \Npleasure beyond even sexual gratification.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし　今は それが裏目に出ている。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We still have over half a day \Nbefore the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:06.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲームが世に出て １０年以上。 この煮詰まった状況を 打破しない限り
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:06.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I use my nose to track the intruder, we can find the bomb with time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:11.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺りくは　繰り返される。 だから俺達が　ピリオドを打つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:11.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we have proof when we report to the \NRoyal Guard, we'll look much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:15.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}同志を募り　ゲームを攻略する。 協力してほしい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:15.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we save the King's life, they'll be quite grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:22.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カードを得る方法は？ １　自力探索　２　トレード
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:22.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right? Yes... That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:26.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３　奪取…　どれになるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:26.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As soon as I find the bomb, I'll contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:36.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}厳密に言えば ３つとも全部使うが 特に３が重要ってことだろ？ 何だよ　じゃあ　結局 力ずくで奪うのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:36.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The coward finally calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:42.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}違う！　少なくとも 俺達は暴力を使わない！ スペル。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:42.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm getting closer to becoming \Nthe King behind the scenes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:50.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スペルの中のカードを 奪うスペル。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:50.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Seven minutes to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを防御するスペルがあるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll give a call when it's down to one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのスペルカードを 俺達が独占する。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Assemble near the exit then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プレーヤーを悩ませ続けた カード化限度枚数
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Until then, stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを逆手にとる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meleoron, about your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他にクリアする方法は　ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:08.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}過去　いろいろなプレーヤーに 会ったが　結論は同じ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:08.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll tap your shoulder ten seconds \Nbefore I need to breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:11.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カードを求めても 結局　奪われてしまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:11.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And then, I'll tap you again when \NI start to hold my breath again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:16.57,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　このゲームの前提が カードの奪い合いだからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:16.57,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You don't need to push your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奪われるリスクを 限りなくゼロにし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should catch your breath \Nwhenever you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:25.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確実にカードを奪う。 あんた達　肝心なこと 言ってないだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:25.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When God's Accomplice isn't active, \Nyou can trust me to handle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:33.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君達　バッテラ氏の依頼で ここに参加したんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:33.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why don't you have a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.57,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}承知の上での勧誘か。 ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.57,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you underestimate their sense \Nof smell, you'll die quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:43.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達も　バッテラ氏に雇われて プレーしている。 故に　クリア報酬は５００億。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:43.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tracking someone by the smell of \Ncigarette smoke is simple for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを仲間全員で山分けする。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We could be knocked out the \Nsecond I take my first breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}現在　仲間は５３名。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The boss will be putting up a smokescreen \Nwhen we go in. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:56.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残り必要なスペルカード集めに２か月 勝負に出て１か月 ３か月でクリアだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:56.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I know, but I'd rather avoid unnecessary risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もちろん　仲間に入ってくれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't want to regret my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君達に　今　かかっている スペルも解除する。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Royal Guard is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:09.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}入るぜ。 ５００億を山分けってのは 正直キツいが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:09.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The three of them gathered above the \Nfront gate to discuss something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:13.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３か月でクリアっていう 期限つきが気に入った。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:13.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou stayed there, and Youpi went back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんたは　どうだい？ 一つ　聞くが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pouf returned to the air to scatter his scales, so I don't think anything has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:22.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}例えば　俺が入手難度ＳＳのカードを 単独でゲットしたら　報酬は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:22.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll let you know if anything else happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:27.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もちろん　そのランクなら ５億で取引している。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:27.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, until we leave, feed us as \Nmuch information as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:32.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＯＫ　入ろう。 君達は　どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:32.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Essentially, that eliminates the \Npossibility of the Royal Guard being out of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:36.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　ごめん。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:36.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Essentially, but not completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:43.09,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？　何が？ 俺は　いい 自力でプレーするから。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:43.09,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, I guarantee that they'll be near the King. You can't guarantee anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We have to be prepared for any possibility, or we'll be slow to react when \Nsomething goes wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:49.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}リーダーが　そう言うんでね 俺もパス。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:49.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You only say that because you don't \Nunderstand how loyal they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　ゴン！　待てってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's impossible that they'd leave the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君は　どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Royal Guard is always with the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}では　まず スペル解除のため
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And it's fine to believe that! But we should prepare for any exceptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:04.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君達には　一度 ゲームの外に出てもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:04.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Give me an example of one \Nof these exceptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:09.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームに戻って来たら　そのまま スタート地点で待機しててくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:09.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Honestly, how can they be having \Na dispute at the last second?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こちらから　迎えに行く。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One exception could be a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:17.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし　フリーポケットに カードがあれば 今のうちに渡してもらおう。 なぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:17.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Isn't one of the King's objectives to reproduce?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:21.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームの外に出たら フリーポケットのカードデータは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:21.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wasn't sure what the King was doing in \Nthe palace, but he was reproducing. That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全て消えてしまうんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:28.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確か　指定ポケットのほうは 出し入れする際 オートセーブされるんだよなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:28.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That would give the King a reason to keep \Nthe Royal Guard from his bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:37.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ　だが１０日以内に 戻って来ないと データは消滅する。 君達が　その期限内に 戻って来なければ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:37.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Perhaps Bizeff was bringing \Nwomen in for the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}リタイアしたものとみなす いいね？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Palm and the King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫　仲間が迎えに来た。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're sticking to the plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}使うのは　「リーブ」のカードだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gon has no idea what they're talking about. I'm glad we realized this before we set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:19:00.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　ゴンってばよ。 どういうことだか説明しろよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:19:00.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we'd seen something like \Nthat without warning, we'd have frozen in our tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Get it now? You can never overthink something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:08.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ごめんね　キルア！　どうしても 我慢できなくなっちゃって。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:08.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are probably other unexpected \Nsituations that we haven't considered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:13.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　だから　「ごめん」の意味 分かんねえって。 だって　これで キルアのスペルは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:13.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, something is still bothering me. Gon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}当分　かかりっ放しに なっちゃったし。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:20.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だ　んなことか 別に問題ねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:20.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let Palm take care of herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　俺の親父捜しのために
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No matter what you see, \Nyou must stay focused on Pitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:31.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアにもゲームに 参加してもらってるのに…。 違うよ　俺がゲームに 参加してるのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:31.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah! It bothers me, but whether \Na woman's involved or not, I believe we should be prepared \Nfor a third party in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それよか　さっき 何で怒ってたんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have a feeling that the third party is causing my anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:40.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だって　あいつら ジンの作ったゲームを 殺りくだとか 奪い合いが前提だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:40.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why did the King injure himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}悪いふうにばっか言うんだもん。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hold on... That was just a theory of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:47.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　ジンの言う通り このゲームを楽しもうと思った。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:47.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, but you agreed that there \Nwas no other logical explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:52.58,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スタート地点に立った時 確かに　ひと筋縄では行かないと 思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:52.58,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're contradicting yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは ゲームに参加している　みんなが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Didn't you say there could be other exceptions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:20:03.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}真剣にゲームを 楽しんでると思ったから。 実際に人が死んでるけど 怖いのは　ゲームじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:20:03.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Following that logic, Pitou could have stopped using En \Nfor other, unexpected reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プレーヤーの考え方だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I understand that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:12.57,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他の人を傷つけてまで カードを取ろうとするなんて。 そうか？　俺は　ありだと思うぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:12.57,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But something doesn't feel right. With three minutes left to go, is this \Nsomething worth thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　本気で言ってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だからこその ハンター専用ゲームだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:22.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも…。 殺しは　なしさ 俺だって　そこは賛成だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:22.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When would you try to hurt yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:31.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝ったほうが相手のカードを もらえるってのは　どうだ？ あっ　ありだ。 なっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:31.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I couldn't forgive myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:35.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺に　スペルをかけた奴だって あの連中の作戦だって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:35.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When you couldn't forgive yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームとして　まっとうな やり方だと思うぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's the logical conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:46.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。 やり方は　ハメみたいで カッコ悪いけどな。 まっ　とにかく あんな奴らは　ほっといて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:46.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that would mean the King \Nis a ruler with personal pride, and not just a cold tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:54.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達は　ゲームを楽しもうぜ。 キルア。 ん？ ありがと！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:54.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}True. For the sake of his pride, he's willing to endure pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:58.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアと一緒に ここに来られて…　ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:58.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Speaking from experience, people like him will never \Nbe willing to compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:02.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアと会えて 俺　本当に　よかったよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:02.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If the leader refuses to compromise, \Nneither will the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:08.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やめろよ　バカ　恥ずいだろ。 何で？　俺　ホントに そう思ってるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:08.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should assume that combat \Nwill be our only option!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:15.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逆だよ…　ゴン　俺なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:15.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Morel was able to sum everything up... But he's wrong. The King's self-injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:21.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺のほうこそ　お前に会えて 本当に　よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:21.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The third party... We still haven't correctly \Ndeduced what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:25.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど　そういう訳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:25.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:31.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それにしても　いいわねぇ 若い男の子の無垢な友情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:31.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that the truth has the potential \Nto completely ruin our plans! It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:36.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なんか　むちゃくちゃに してやりたい気分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:36.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One minute to go. Gather around.
